<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/382111-in-the-first-chapter-the-miniaturist">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[In the first chapter, the Miniaturist places one last piece for the dolls house on Marin's gravestone in order 'to complete what she started'. At the very end of the book, the significance of that final miniature is revealed and we know who it represents, BUT I would love to know what happens next! A sequel, perhaps? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
